You are on a boat. It is on fire.
[[stay on the boat->stay]]
[[jump into the water->water]]


:: stay {"position":"443,322.5","size":"100,100"}
Did I mention the boat was ''ON FIRE?''

This was a short adventure for you.
[[start over->start]]


:: swim2 {"position":"110,783.5","size":"100,100"}
You try to swim out to the boat, but it is farther than you thought.
...and swimming is hard when you've barely eaten.
You slowly sink below the waves.
[[start over->start]] 



